                                                    <img width="55" height="55" src="https://www.learnworlds.com/app/uploads/2026/04/Essential-LMS-reports-to-track-employee-training-and-measure-impact-70x70.jpg" class="block obj-fit-cover h-full rounded-light wp-post-image" alt="a woman looking at course statistics" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.learnworlds.com/app/uploads/2026/04/Essential-LMS-reports-to-track-employee-training-and-measure-impact-70x70.jpg 70w, https://www.learnworlds.com/app/uploads/2026/04/Essential-LMS-reports-to-track-employee-training-and-measure-impact-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 55px) 100vw, 55px" />                                            </div>
                    <a class="lw-txt lw-txt-s semi-bold mb-0" href="https://www.learnworlds.com/blog/business/lms-reports-track-employee-training/"><span class="js-t-title">Essential LMS reports to track employee training and measure impact</span></a>
                </li>
